channel.title: Webclient can't connect only at Windows 7
channel.description: Hi, I've made a webclient useing Ric's webclient tutorial. Everthing works. I can log in on win xp, ubuntu and vista but not on windows 7. I've done portforwarding correctly and http://www.canyouseeme.org says he can see my service. I think it's something with Windows firewall but'I've opened 43594 already for incoming and outgoing. Does anyone knows what's wrong?
